{"tid":1655584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全民緊急任務 全民文宣重現百萬人遊行","createTime":"2019-10-15T06:37:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T06:43:55.000Z","uid":7716,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ee4719f8a6f50657264be39d64078ef9a3286438","tid":1655584,"uid":7716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:37:11.000Z","msg":"知唔知一百萬人遊行<br />\n二百萬人遊行前我地係做緊咩？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係文宣呀！</span></strong></span><br />\n你會係個陣見到有好多人派傳單<br />\n係連儂牆會見到全部都係遊行文宣<br />\n你想人去大遊行<br />\n都要比人感覺當日個勢係好大<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第一步 就係宣傳攻勢</span></span><br />\n各位好嬲左好多日嘅人<br />\n又覺得無嘢做到<br />\n其實印嘢組隊去派就得<br />\n去痴牆都可以<br />\n依家18區都有gp<br />\n真心求和理非出多一分力<br />\n我希望見到每日都會見到1020文宣出現<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第二步 就係social media </span></span><br />\n我知好多人都做緊<br />\n繼續洗1020遊行文宣<br />\n唔好以為自己無影響你<br />\n多你一個就係好多<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第三步 口號</span></span><br />\n黎緊所有活動都要嗌1020見<br />\n10點鳩嗌都要嗌<br />\n要令到今次聲勢浩大<br />\n<br />\n時間無多啦咁多位<br />\n唔想做革命free rider<br />\n係呢刻諗下可以做啲咩<br />\n做左先 做完先知成效<br />\n如果唔係對得住死左嘅手足咩？<br />\n如果唔係對得住比人拉左嘅手足咩？<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n香港人 革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67af9813c63837301fffb9f5d0bec1a5d6d088ee","tid":1655584,"uid":7716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:38:14.000Z","msg":"今晚就痴佢老母牆"},{"pid":"1f9cdf28f84b7078199930e56247f9835e153019","tid":1655584,"uid":198590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:38:15.000Z","msg":"幫你推<br />\n<br />\n等我為大家回憶下決定1020去定唔去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1655497\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1655497</a>"},{"pid":"bcba9d78c065b5d145fc6d14f368658033e4af14","tid":1655584,"uid":7716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:38:26.000Z","msg":"無人痴我自己痴"},{"pid":"0e60b109924a5c859a12c1eb497a53cfcdd6d2d7","tid":1655584,"uid":7716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:38:43.000Z","msg":"和理非升級！"},{"pid":"69261fc53db8d9210786e1a199c90e8a403f6d4a","tid":1655584,"uid":7716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:38:56.000Z","msg":"和勇不分！"},{"pid":"485b92d7d7dad44a91d90eee173349111ebaac86","tid":1655584,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:39:00.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n［第九期牆紙］四色分類，你我做到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1647496/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1647496/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9CWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=11900e1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n歡迎投稿 : <a href=\"https://padlet.com/lennonnewshk/6g5yp3tllkxx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpadlet.com%2Flennonnewshk%2F6g5yp3tllkxx&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9CWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=9d272c1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://padlet.com/lennonnewshk/6g5yp3tllkxx</a>"},{"pid":"131335be263bb1f29114e2a71069a280a4145d60","tid":1655584,"uid":7716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:39:23.000Z","msg":"要自己派單"},{"pid":"37489512ba8be325dd181710c2a35d6a75b86fbb","tid":1655584,"uid":7716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:41:03.000Z","msg":"點推得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"758b0d94b723e5237b59fe288014c3b6ef651f03","tid":1655584,"uid":255150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:41:10.000Z","msg":"我宣布 連登正式死亡